OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 13 APR
OL,4,G2150FMozart's Women: A Musical Journey
OL,5,     GA night of unforgettable music
OL,6,     Gand performance. Filmed live at
OL,7,     Gthe London Coliseum, Mozart's
OL,8,     GWomen features performances from
OL,9,     Gsome of opera's brightest stars.
OL,10,G2320FComedy Legends: Lucille Ball
OL,11,     GBarry Cryer fondly looks back at
OL,12,     Gthe life and career of the comedy
OL,13,     Gsuperstar who created the highly
OL,14,     Ginfluential I Love Lucy among
OL,15,     Gmany other popular sitcoms.
OL,16,G0020FHendrix & Handel: Urban Myths
OL,17,     GJimi Hendrix and his girlfriend
OL,18,     Gmove into their first home in
OL,19,     GLondon - which turns out to be
OL,20,     Gthe same building that George
OL,21,     GFrideric Handel lived in 246
OL,22,     Gyears prior. David Haig stars.
